title: Sara McLachlan-The Freedom Sessions, Classic Records Gold CD
description: This is the companion record to 'Fumbling Towards Ecstacy'and also is much improved on this now-deleted Classic Records version. This is more of a demo-takes collection and has much less in the way of production. Ice for instance has her vocal accompanied by just (I think) a Les Paul plugged into a Marshall with the volume set at '11'. But it works!
